<li id="cite_note-Concerning_the_C_in_the_SCA-18"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Concerning_the_C_in_the_SCA_18-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFFriedmanCook.2C_Elizabeth1988">Friedman, David; Cook, Elizabeth (1988). <a href="http://www.pbm.com/~lindahl/cariadoc/concerning_the_c_in_sca.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pbm.com/~lindahl/cariadoc/concerning_the_c_in_sca.html" rel="nofollow">"Concerning the 'C' in SCA"</a>. Greg Lindahl<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.pbm.com/~lindahl/cariadoc/concerning_the_c_in_sca.html" class="external free" title="http://www.pbm.com/~lindahl/cariadoc/concerning_the_c_in_sca.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.pbm.com/~lindahl/cariadoc/concerning_the_c_in_sca.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 7 June 2007</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Concerning+the+%27C%27+in+SCA&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Friedman&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft.au=Friedman%2C+David&amp;rft.au=Cook%2C+Elizabeth&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.pub=Greg+Lindahl&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbm.com%2F%7Elindahl%2Fcariadoc%2Fconcerning_the_c_in_sca.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Society_for_Creative_Anachronism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-The_Dream-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-The_Dream_19-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFClark1993">Clark, Susan (21 March 1993). <a href="http://www.florilegium.org/files/SCA-SOCIOLOGY/SCA-The-Dream-msg.html" class="external text" title="http://www.florilegium.org/files/SCA-SOCIOLOGY/SCA-The-Dream-msg.html" rel="nofollow">"The Dream"</a>. Mark S. Harris<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.florilegium.org/files/SCA-SOCIOLOGY/SCA-The-Dream-msg.html" class="external free" title="http://www.florilegium.org/files/SCA-SOCIOLOGY/SCA-The-Dream-msg.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.florilegium.org/files/SCA-SOCIOLOGY/SCA-The-Dream-msg.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 7 June 2007</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Dream&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Clark&amp;rft.aufirst=Susan&amp;rft.au=Clark%2C+Susan&amp;rft.date=21+March+1993&amp;rft.pub=Mark+S.+Harris&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.florilegium.org%2Ffiles%2FSCA-SOCIOLOGY%2FSCA-The-Dream-msg.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Society_for_Creative_Anachronism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
